                </p>
                <p class="article-text">Your regular Zerodha or Groww account? They only give you access to Indian
                    stocks. Want to buy Nvidia? Good luck.</p>
                <blockquote class="article-quote">
                    <p>"I tried buying Tesla shares on my Zerodha account. Spent 30 minutes searching before I
                        realized... you can't. I needed a completely different broker for US stocks."</p>
                    <footer>‚Äî Rahul, Bangalore (frustrated investor)</footer>
                </blockquote>
                <p class="article-text">This article solves that problem once and for all. We'll compare every single
                    broker that gives Indians access to US markets, break down the REAL costs, and tell you exactly
                    which one to choose based on YOUR investing style.</p>
